 jeans that have helped make him a household name     once upon a time  the idea of differentiating things by label made sense  now it doesn   t seem right     he says     there can be a broader range of things we make under one  name  i make accessories  i make clothes  i work on cosmetics and fragrances  it   s all a palette for women to tell the story of who they want to be    
